Subject: [PATCH] ==== update probe hits for new monitoring parameters ====

mm/damon: update probe hits for runtime parameters commits

DAMON users can update DAMON parameters such as samplling and
aggregation intervals at runtime.  For such changes, monitoring results
that depend on the parameters need to be properly updated.  For example,
the accesss freqeuency counter (nr_accesses) is updated so.  The data
attribute monitoring counter (probe_hits) is not beinng updted.  Do the
updates for new parameters.

Signed-off-by: SJ Park <sj@kernel.org>
---
 hkml_cv_bogus/hkml_cv_bogus_z5liib0q | 0
 1 file changed, 0 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)
 create mode 100644 hkml_cv_bogus/hkml_cv_bogus_z5liib0q

diff --git a/hkml_cv_bogus/hkml_cv_bogus_z5liib0q b/hkml_cv_bogus/hkml_cv_bogus_z5liib0q
